00:10:25,295 --> 00:10:29,845
ふたり笑い出してる
The two of us start laughing

161
00:10:30,045 --> 00:10:33,295
いつまでもまっすぐに
Always straight ahead

162
00:10:33,445 --> 00:10:36,845
眼差しはあるように
May our gaze remain

163
00:10:37,095 --> 00:10:40,145
汗が滲んでも
Even if sweat seeps through

164
00:10:40,295 --> 00:10:45,345
手を離さないよ
I won't let go of your hand

165
00:10:45,895 --> 00:10:48,845
ずっと
Forever

166
00:10:49,045 --> 00:10:52,445
消える飛行機雲
The vanishing contrail

167
00:10:52,595 --> 00:10:56,545
僕たちは見送った
We watched it go

168
00:10:56,695 --> 00:11:00,395
眩しくて逃げた
It was so bright we ran away

169
00:11:00,495 --> 00:11:04,245
いつだって弱くて
Always weak

170
00:11:05,495 --> 00:11:10,095
あの日から変わらず
Unchanged since that day

171
00:11:10,195 --> 00:11:14,195
いつまでも変わらずに
Forever unchanged

172
00:11:14,345 --> 00:11:17,845
いられなかったこと
That we couldn't stay that way

173
00:11:17,995 --> 00:11:21,295
悔しくて指を
Frustratedly, my fingers...

174
00:11:21,395 --> 00:11:31,045
離す
...let go

175
00:12:21,045 --> 00:12:41,545
獅白ぼたん アイドル衣装
Shishiro Botan: Idol Costume

